    @Value
public class Size
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<Size>
    A class of sizes involving an x component and a y component.
    Version:
    1.2
    Author:
    Simon Merckx and Tobias Cornille
    Invariants:
  • Each size can have its x component as x component.
         canHaveAsXComponent(this.getXComponent())
  • Each size can have its y component as y component.
         canHaveAsYComponent(this.getYComponent())
